# The Gang of Four
- Seperate out the things that change from those that stay the same
  將可能改變的東西與保持不變的東西分開
  A key goal of software engineering is to build systems that allow us to contain the damage
- Progeram to an interface, not an implementation (loosely coupling code)
  classify common traits and behaviors

The proper use of design pattern is the art of making your system just flexible enough to
deal with the problems you have today, but no more. 
